# GIT WORKFLOW

## Branch Strategy (Tree)

```
ideate/{{TAG}}                 <- main branch (best version)
+-- ideate/{{TAG}}/A           <- direction A
|   +-- ideate/{{TAG}}/A.1    <- sub-refinement
+-- ideate/{{TAG}}/B
+-- ideate/{{TAG}}/C
```

## Commit Conventions

Format: `<type>(<scope>): <what and why>`

Types: `seed`, `survey`, `validate`, `direction`, `decide`, `dead-end`, `refs`, `converge`, `checkpoint`, `auto`

