# WORKSPACE FILES

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `config.md` | Global constraints, eval weights, auto params |
| `refs.db` | Paper database (SQLite + FTS5) |
| `scripts/refs.py` | Reference DB CLI |
| `scripts/status.py` | Compact status generator |
| `doc/agent/sketch.md` | Current state & next steps |
| `doc/agent/idea_versions/` | Idea cards, one per version |
| `doc/agent/directions/` | Direction evaluation reports |
| `doc/agent/validations/` | Detailed validation reports |
| `doc/agent/findings.md` | Patterns, dead ends, insights |
| `doc/agent/decisions.md` | Direction and pivot decisions |
| `doc/proposals/evaluation.md` | Accumulated evaluation history (user-facing) |
| `doc/proposals/draft.md` | Current proposal snapshot (user-facing) |

