# QUICK REFERENCE

```bash
python3 scripts/status.py                         # Full status + tree
python3 scripts/status.py --tree-only              # Just the tree
python3 scripts/refs.py search "query"             # Find papers
python3 scripts/refs.py stats                      # Reference DB overview
python3 scripts/refs.py links A.1                  # Papers for a version
git log --graph --oneline -15 --show-notes --all   # Git history
```

